data.description: A really sweet find in Silver Lake. This spacious 1,468 square foot home will give you all the room you want plus lightness and brightness galore from the many well placed windows. You will enjoy a well appointed kitchen with all newer appliances and lots of extra cabinets (an avid cook's dream). The spacious great room boasts an attractive architectural surprise along one wall and the dining room boasts a built-in hutch and delightful chandelier. Double doors lead to a large Master bedroom with a walk-in closet and an en-suite also behind double doors. The en-suite includes a lovely vanity area, a large linen closet, and separate commode/shower room. The second bedroom also includes a walk-in closet and the second bathroom is equally well appointed. Some bonuses included in this home are the large Florida room under heat and air, the laundry/work shop space also under heat and air and the neat golf cart enclosure. Looking upward, you will see vaulted ceilings in most rooms plus an invincible life time roof. This home sits high on a very attractive street and is close to all the great conveniences offered in The Villages. This meticulous home has indeed been lovingly maintained. NO BOND
